@NODE "Bugs" "Bugs"
@TOC "MAIN"

	@{b}Known Bugs and Limitations@{ub}


	° In node names, some character will be converted to their
	  &xxx; replacement. There is no work around at the moment.
	  The &xxx; replacement should not make further problems.

	° There should be a problem with links, that cross line
	  bounderies. Even Multiview has problems with this, so
	  @{b}don't expect@{ub} a work around soon!

	If you discover some kind of bug or limitation please feel
	free to send a comment to the @{"author" LINK "Author"}.

@ENDNODE
